<HEADLINE> CPPCC Vice-Chairman Meets Cambodian Prince </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 25 (Xinhua)-- Li Guixian, vice-chairman of the
National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC), met with Cambodian Prince Norodom Sirivudh
today.
</P>
