<HEADLINE> S.African President Welcomes Visiting Chinese President Jiang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRETORIA, April 25 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Chinese President Jiang
Zemin and his wife Wang Yeping were warmly welcomed by South
African President Thabo Mbeki at a welcome ceremony here on
Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Jiang and Mbeki extended warm greetings to each other at the
ceremony on the square in front of the Presidential Office.
</P>
