maintaining political stability and developing economy are the
three major tasks faced by the country at present.
</P>
<P>
Nazarbayev made the remarks in an interview with local official
press on the occasion of the 10th anniversary of the country's
presidential system, the Interfax news agency reported.
</P>
<P>
