the four-day Easter Parade in Germany, which brought thousands of
people together in some 60 German cities.
</P>
<P>
Organizers said that during this year's Easter Parade, which
coincided with the anniversary of NATO's bombing against
Yugoslavia, paraders were more united in demanding: "No war, No
German soldiers abroad, and No military exports."
