military spending" were frequently seen in the procession.
</P>
<P>
In Stuttgart, paraders blocked the exit for the general command
for U.S. troops in Europe for several hours.
</P>
<P>
The Easter peace march originated in Great Britain 40 years ago,
and it is now held annually in Europe. 
