<HEADLINE> Peru to Reclaim 59 Archeological Pieces from Canada </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Peru will take back a group of pre-
Colombian archeological pieces seized by Canadian authorities in
1985, the National Institute of Culture (NIC) said Monday.
</P>
