<TEXT>
<P>
PRETORIA, April 25 (Xinhua) -- South African President Thabo
Mbeki said here on Tuesday that his country and China are united
by a common resolve to build a better life for themselves.
</P>
<P>
Mbeki said at a banquet he hosted in honor of visiting Chinese
President Jiang Zemin: "We are at one in the commitment to ensure
that we build that better life in conditions of freedom and
peace."
</P>
<P>
